All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable, Measure<LastEvaluationMeasure.Evaluation<Solution,​Value>>, PushMeasure<LastEvaluationMeasure.Evaluation<Solution,​Value>>, DescribedEntity
public class LastEvaluationMeasure<Solution,​Value>
extends SimplePushMeasure<LastEvaluationMeasure.Evaluation<Solution,​Value>>
LastEvaluationMeasure is a PushMeasure providing the last evaluation made in an algorithm. It extends SimplePushMeasure and add the method push(Object, Object) for simplicity.
